{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5b30d25a41","title":"毛泽东撰介绍麻城的经验","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"151fe36156","index":0,"year":1959,"month":4,"day":2,"articleId":"5b30d25a41"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4a8bbb980f","type":"title","text":"毛泽东撰介绍麻城的经验","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"8fc1867bd4","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"b94c45576f","type":"paragraph","text":"这几个文件都值得看。特别是《麻城县万人大会的情况》，值得看，办法很好，县、社两级该退还的，迅速地退还给生产队了，一身清净，然后进而解决队与社员的矛盾，公社就可以大大地发展起来。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"3142d35bf8","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一九五九年四月二日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"9c979343ad","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"b95ff1160d","type":"paragraph","text":"此件极好，每一个县、社都应这样做。算帐才能团结；算帐才能帮助干部从贪污浪费的海洋中拔出身来，一身清净；算帐才能教会干部学会经营管理方法；算帐才能教会五亿农民自己管理自己的公社，监督公社的各级干部只许办好事，不许办坏事，实现群众的监督，实现真正的民主集中制。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"ce0617d646","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一九五九年四月三日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"662c2299e9","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"b420ba69e1","type":"paragraph","text":"此件连前两件，中央、省、地、县委书记、委员人人必读，各县、社都应仿照办理。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"e2ea0a5808","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一九五九年四月三日下午","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"f8060121a7","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"},{"id":"5cca6ed8ac","type":"paragraph","text":"毛注：是在于毁坏社会主义事业，是在于毁坏合作社和人民公社，是在于毁坏干部自身。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41"}],"page":{"id":"ba9528498e","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5b30d25a41","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}